Package: LinguaR
Type: Package
Title: LinguaR is a package that provides translation functions for R users.
Version: 0.1.0
Author: "Viten"
Maintainer: The package maintainer <vitenmarti@gmail.com>
Description: LinguaR is a package that provides translation functions for R users. It is designed to help users easily translate text from one language to another, with support for multiple translation services and languages.
